attributedDescription.content: Mecha king ghidorah time travels teleportation to 1992 to fight godzilla and stop him from destroying all of japan. As you can see godzilla is not happy about king ghidorah being back as he goes right for shooting at ghidorah with his atomic breath, but buildings are in the way, and mecha king ghidorah gets a really cool first scene.
